<![CDATA[<h1></h1><p>Author: D-Sketon(xxx@example.com)</p>
        
          <h1 id="configure--the-firefox-to-hide-tab-bar-address-bar-adn-bookmark-bar">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#configure--the-firefox-to-hide-tab-bar-address-bar-adn-bookmark-bar"></a>
Configure  the firefox to hide TAB bar, address bar adn bookmark bar
</h1><h2 id="enable-css-support">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#enable-css-support"></a>
Enable CSS support
</h2><ol>
<li>Type &ldquo;about: config&rdquo; in the <em>Firefox</em> address bar and then press the <code>Enter</code> key</li>
<li>Accept the risk and move on</li>
<li>Search <code>toolkit.legacyUserProfileCustomizations.stylesheets</code></li>
<li>Make sure its value is set to <code>true</code>.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="find-and-create-the-css-file">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#find-and-create-the-css-file"></a>
Find and create the CSS file
</h2><ol>
<li>Type &ldquo;about: support&rdquo; in the <em>Firefox</em> and press <code>Enter</code>.</li>
<li>Find the line &ldquo;Profile Folder&rdquo; and open it</li>
<li>Check if there is a folder named <code>chrome</code>. if not ,create it.</li>
<li>Create a file <code>userChrome.css</code> including the following code.</li>
</ol>
